<div id="pfdc5" class="pf w0 h12d" data-page-no="dc5"><div class="pc pcdc5 w0 h12d"><div class="t mde0 x28 hc4 y1dab ff1 fs3b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">TRUE EDUCATION </div><div class="t m7e1 x28 hc4 y19d1 ff1 fs3b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READER SERIES </div><div class="t m715 x19 h99 y1310 ff7 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Books One to Seven </div><div class="t m1741 xc5 h4 y1fd9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As the first years of school life have the greatest </div><div class="t m5cf x74 h4 y1c68 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">influence on the character of the child, much care should </div><div class="t mac9 x74 h4 y19d4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be used in selecting the reading lessons to be placed in </div><div class="t m5fe x74 h4 yecd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the hands of the pupil. The vital, living truths con-</div><div class="t m84f x74 h4 y138e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tained in the Scriptures are essential to the formation </div><div class="t m118b x48 h4 y1db5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.of sound characters; therefore the lessons in the first </div><div class="t meff x74 h4 y1106 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">three Readers are quite largely developed from Bible </div><div class="t m1a1 x74 h4 y1e9b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">themes, in story form. </div><div class="t m71f x61 h32 y1e6b ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">. THE FIRST READER </div><div class="t m1585 x2f h4 y1e6b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gives the story in a very </div><div class="t m1833 x74 h4 y1191 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">simple style, fixing upon the child&apos;s mind in his first </div><div class="t m80f x74 h4 y1342 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">school year the beautiful Gospel story from Creation to </div><div class="t m2eb x74 h4 y12ae ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Redemption. </div><div class="t m119c xc h32 y14ce ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE SECOND READER </div><div class="t m249 x3b h4 y1cb0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">follows the same general </div><div class="t m5ea x73 h4 y14df ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">line, with several additional topics especially interesting </div><div class="t m7c2 x74 h4 y14d1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to children. </div><div class="t m12b0 xb hd9 yd4d ff7 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Continued on Previous Page </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
